content:
Watches for changes to SCSS/Sass files and automatically compiles them to CSS. Includes source map generation for debugging and minification for production builds.

```json
{
  "PostToolUse": [
    {
      "matcher": "Edit|Write",
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.scss ]] || [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.sass ]]; then echo 'ðŸŽ¨ Compiling SCSS...' && npx sass \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" \"${CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH%.s[ac]ss}.css\" --source-map && echo 'âœ… SCSS compiled successfully'; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
